24 int italic;
25 int em;
26 int x_height;
27 int fig_height;
28 int cap_height;
29 int asc_height;
30 int body_height;
31 int comma_depth;
32 int desc_depth;
33 int body_depth;
34};

36struct char_metric {
37 int width;
38 int type;
39 int height;
40 int depth;
41 int ic;

44};
